{"tid":1573695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"盧偉聰：警員展現高度專業，是香港最後一道防線","createTime":"2019-09-16T05:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T09:37:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1263584253c4f05d54d7415897e4cecb5c124853","tid":1573695,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"警務處長盧偉聰向警員發公告，讚揚警隊每一位成員在極度艱難的時刻，仍然展現高度專業，堅守崗位及勇敢面對危險，對此表示敬意和感謝；又說警隊是守護香港的第一道、亦是最後一道防線，會努力奮戰恢復社會秩序。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰又指反修例示威已經持續一百日，在警隊歷史上留下不能磨滅的印記，暴力程度亦不斷升級，更有人作出針對警隊的行為，嚴重衝擊香港的法治，破壞社會秩序及安寜。他指深深體會到警員面對極大的危險和壓力，會因為執行職務期間被無理謾罵、指控和惡意中傷，而感到無奈和委屈，警隊管理層會在各方面採取一切可行措施支援。"},{"pid":"9712ec012a94199f9a85326389afc388a0551ec7","tid":1573695,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1172290&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1172290%26csid%3D261_341&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xfuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=c2cc848e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1172290&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"039b187ee6c74d6b70f6a134e81726d57c6483e1","tid":1573695,"uid":254551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"仲有黑社會個一度，放心"},{"pid":"ea897cae59c3fb09e7ab573eaa6d48d7b2478fa7","tid":1573695,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBfJ3Kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBfJ3Kt.jpg&h=035c3ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">宣佈 和你suck 4.0 9月22 星期日見<br />\n<br />\nsuck 4.0 將會基於 hkmap.live 行動  <br />\n麻煩力推呢個livemap <br />\n對各位日後行動都非常大幫助<br />\n<br />\n請各位必須係 9月22日當日12點30分留意channel / 連登 / IG 最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/